  "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
  "body": "Currently we have no way to change the URL for a repository:\n\n```\n$ bin/helm repo add test http://charts.test.com\nError: The repository name you provided (test) already exists. Please specify a different name.\n```\n\nIt would be nice for scripting purposes for `helm repo add` to be able to update repository details (if that repository has already been registered):\n\n```\n$ bin/helm repo add --update test http://charts.test.com\ntest has been updated\n```\n",
